app.name: RealTechee-Gen2
app.buildSpec:
version: 1
frontend:
  phases:
    preBuild:
      commands:
        - npm ci
    build:
      commands:
        - if [ ! -d "./public/meta" ]; then mkdir -p public/meta; fi
        - echo "Building RealTechee version $(node -p
          "require('./package.json').version")"
        - echo "NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_VERSION=$(node -p
          "require('./package.json').version")" >> .env.local
        - echo "{\"version\":\"$(node
          -p   "require('./package.json').version")\",\"buildTime\":\"$(date -u
          +"%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ")\",\"gitCommit\":\"$(git rev-parse --short
          HEAD)\"}" >  ./public/meta/build-info.json
        - npm run build
  artifacts:
    baseDirectory: .next
    files:
      - "**/*"
    discard-paths: false
  cache:
    paths:
      - node_modules/**/*
